items.name: Breadsticks
items.description: These are not your cookie cutter store bought bread sticks. We make our breadsticks fresh everyday which are absolutely delicious. Smothered in 'Dock butter' and dusted with our famous fairy dust. Hard to eat just one!

items.name: Nacho Supreme
items.description: Our tri-colored chips, loads of nacho cheese, ground beef, black olives, diced tomatoes, jalapeno peppers, sour cream drizzle and topped with chives.

items.name: Fried Clam Strips
items.description: Delectable strips of clam lightly breaded and served with choice of sauce.

items.name: River Bread
items.description: House made blue cheese spread smothered on top of our delicious 10" French artisan baguette.

items.name: Catfish Curls
items.description: We take one of our catfish filets and cut it up into strips, deep fry and serve 'em with choice of sauce.

items.name: Garlic Bread with Cheese
items.description: We top our 10" artisan French baguette with 'Dock butter' and loads of our 'Special Grande' cheese.

items.name: Chicken Tenders
items.description: 4 strips served with a side of fries.

items.name: Garlic Bread
items.description: We top our 10" artisan French baguette with 'Dock butter' and baked to perfection! A house favorite!

items.name: Potato Boats
items.description: Enjoy this Dock favorite! We make our own and we like ours with lots of potato!! Filled in with nacho cheese bacon bits, topped with chives and sour cream.

items.name: Pig Cracklin's
items.description: Something no one else has!! Some call 'em pork rinds, we call 'em Cracklin's! They come to your table 'Cracklin and Poppin'. Try them with one of our great 'rubs' or just plain.

items.name: Wings
items.description: Breaded wings served with your favorite sauce. Try them 'tossed'!

items.name: Basket of Onion Rings
items.description: We make these fresh to order.

items.name: Basket of Breaded Pickles
items.description: A dozen of our sliced kosher pickles, lightly breaded and served with our house made spicy ranch dressing.

items.name: Nachos
items.description: Our tri colored chips, deep fried and smothered in our nacho cheese sauce.

items.name: Chili
items.description: Whitey's famous chili.

items.name: Marinated Chicken Pieces
items.description: Fresh spring mix, tomato slices, cucumber slices, blue cheese crumbles, sliced red onion and fajita chicken strips marinated in balsamic vinaigrette.

items.name: Cobb Salad
items.description: Shredded lettuce, fajita chicken, mushrooms, green peppers, diced tomatoes, bacon crumbles, cheddar cheese and diced egg. Served with choice dressing.

items.name: Side Salad
items.description: Served with choice dressing.

items.name: Garden Salad
items.description: Shredded lettuce, mozzarella cheese, diced tomato, sliced red onion and sliced green pepper. Served with choice dressing.

items.name: Southern Fried Chicken Salad
items.description: Deep fried chicken tenders, shredded lettuce, diced tomato, diced egg and green onion. Served with choice dressing.

items.name: Spring Salad Mix
items.description: Fresh spring mix topped with tomato slices, cucumber slices and sliced red onion. Served with choice dressing.

items.name: Chef Salad
items.description: Shredded lettuce, mozzarella cheese, diced tomato, sliced red onion, sliced green pepper, bacon crumbles and sliced honey baked ham. Served with choice dressing.

items.name: Boneless Buffalo Chicken Salad
items.description: Fresh spring mix topped with bacon crumbles, blue cheese crumbles, crispy tortilla strips, deep fried chicken strips, tossed in mild or hot Buffalo sauce, all tossed in our Pico de gallo. Served with choice dressing.

items.name: Turkey Club Sandwich
items.description: 3 slices wheat bread, turkey slices, tomato, lettuce, American cheese, bacon strips and mayo.

items.name: Chicken Sandwich
items.description: Succulent chicken breast, grilled and topped with your favorite toppings.

items.name: Special Club Sandwich
items.description: Wheat and just like the Turkey Club but we add lots of our Honey Baked Ham slices to turn this sandwich up a notch.

items.name: Tenderloins Sandwich
items.description: Hand pounded, deep fried or grilled, served on our brioche bun with your choice of toppings.

items.name: Catfish Sandwich
items.description: A full filet of our fantastic catfish served on a great brioche bun. Add a side of coleslaw and some tartar sauce and you've got a great meal.

items.name: Cowboy Tenderloin
items.description: Breaded loin topped with crumbled bacon, spicy mayo and pepper jack cheese.

items.name: BLT Sandwich
items.description: Wheat bread, bacon strips, tomato, lettuce and mayo.

items.name: Hot and Spicy Cowboy Tenderloin
items.description: Same great sandwich, but with a KICK.

items.name: Mustang Monster Burger
items.description: 3 hand spanked-patties, 3 slices of cheese, mound of bacon crumbles! Are you adventurous enough for this monster?

items.name: Farmhouse Burger
items.description: Local favorite for all those hard workers! 2 hand-spanked patties, slices of baked honey ham, 3 strips of bacon, your choice of cheese topped with an egg any way you want it! Rich prefers his over easy so the yolk runs down the sandwich.

items.name: Chili Cheddar Burger
items.description: Our hand spanked patties topped with cheddar cheese and our famous chili.

items.name: Horseshoe Burger
items.description: Single patty, served on our artisan French baguette, topped with a pile of shoestring fries and our nacho cheese sauce.

items.name: Mushroom Swiss Burger
items.description: 2 thick slices of Swiss cheese and sauteed mushrooms piled onto our hand-spanked patties, a perennial crowd pleaser.

items.name: Jalapeno Crunch Burger
items.description: Hand spanked double patty, tortilla strips, grilled jalapenos, pico de gallo, chipotle lime mayo, and pepper jack cheese.

items.name: Flight of Sliders Burger
items.description: Four of our hand spanked patties slider sized. Your choice of cheese.

items.name: Mexicali Burger
items.description: Sauteed onions, jalapenos, Pepper Jack cheese sitting a top our hand spanked patties.

items.name: Kahuna Island Burger
items.description: A kitchen favorite! 2 hand spanked patties topped with our house BBQ Sauce, provolone cheese, Honey Baked Ham and loads of crushed pineapple.

items.name: Spicy River Burger
items.description: Our hand spanked patties 'dunked' in Frank's hot or mild sauce topped with our sweet bread and butter pickles and our house made blue cheese spread

items.name: River Burger
items.description: Spicy river burger minus the spice. Delicious in its own right.

items.name: Buffalo Chicken Fries
items.description: Loads of fries, Buffalo fajita chicken, and nacho cheese drizzled with buttermilk ranch.

items.name: Loaded Fries
items.description: A big pile of our french fries covered in nacho cheese topped with bacon and chives and drizzled with sour cream. Comfort food at its' best.

items.name: Chili Fries
items.description: Pile of fries, nacho cheese and our house chili.

items.name: Chicken Bacon Ranch Fries
items.description: Pile of fries, loads of bacon, chives, fajita chicken covered in nacho cheese and drizzled with buttermilk ranch.

items.name: Catfish Dinner
items.description: Tender, flaky fillets served a top our shoestring fries with our house made cole slaw and house made tartar sauce.

items.name: Spicy River Chicken Sandwich
items.description: Delectable chicken breast, grilled and then 'dunked' in Frank's choice of sauce. Topped with our house made blue cheese spread and finished with sweet bread and butter pickles

items.name: River Chicken Sandwich
items.description: Mouth watering chicken breast, grilled then topped with our house made blue cheese spread and finished with sweet bread and butter pickles.

items.name: Special Club Sub
items.description: Honey ham and turkey breast slices with mozzarella cheese, baked to perfection. After baking we top it with shredded lettuce, tomato and mayo.

items.name: Submarine Sub
items.description: Classic Indiana style, a hint of pizza sauce, Genoa salami, honey ham, a bit of red onion and mozzarella cheese.

items.name: Farmhouse BLT Sub
items.description: An American tradition on our delectable 10" artisan baguette, bacon, tomatoes, shredded lettuce and mayo.

items.name: Dock BBQ Sub
items.description: Another Indiana favorite! Piles of our crumbled sausage, generous topping of mozzarella cheese and red onion all topped with Sweet Baby Ray's BBQ.

items.name: Gut Buster Sub
items.description: This one is for our 'adventurous friends'! We start with our special crumbled sausage and our pepperoni, top it with spicy jalapenos, banana peppers, Sweet Baby Ray's BBQ, our zest pizza sauce and loads of melted mozzarella cheese.

items.name: Meat Ball Madness
items.description: We put Chicago made meatballs on our 10" baguette, add mozzarella cheese and top it all off with our zesty pizza sauce.

items.name: Sicilian Sub
items.description: Our version of an East Coast favorite, sliced honey ham, sliced Genoa salami, bacon crumbles, mozzarella cheese, red onion and banana peppers. After it cooks we add shredded lettuce, tomato and douse it with our Italian dressing.

items.name: Stromboli Sub
items.description: An Indiana staple crumbled sausage, red onion, zesty pizza sauce and mozzarella cheese and just a taste of crushed red pepper.

items.name: Veggie Sub
items.description: Colorful and tasty! Tomato, mushrooms, green peppers, banana peppers, red onion and black olives topped with our zesty pizza sauce and mozzarella cheese.

items.name: Buffalo Chicken Sub
items.description: Simple and tasty, Buffalo hot sauce, fajita chicken strips and mozzarella cheese.

items.name: Ham and Cheese Sub
items.description: The bEST ham and cheese you will EVER eat!!! Honey Baked Ham thinly sliced with our grande mozzarella cheese blend and you're all set for a mouth watering feast! Enjoy and you're welcome.

items.name: Chicken Bacon Ranch Sub
items.description: Fajita chicken strips, bacon crumbles, mozzarella cheese and buttermilk ranch.

items.name: BBQ Chicken Sub
items.description: Sweet Baby Ray's BBQ sauce, fajita chicken strips, bacon crumbles, red onion and mozzarella cheese.

items.name: Kid's Tender
items.description: Served with apple sauce.

items.name: Kid's Fish
items.description: Served with apple sauce.

items.name: Kid's Grilled Cheese
items.description: Served with apple sauce.

items.name: Cinnasticks
items.description: Four of our homemade breadsticks baked and topped with butter and dusted with our own cinnamon and sugar blend. Served with a side of icing.
